menu "EGOS SDK"

    config EGOS_ETHERNET_ENABLED
        bool "Enable W5500 Ethernet support"
        default n
        help
            Enable W5500 SPI Ethernet as a network option.
            When enabled, the connection manager tries Ethernet first
            before falling back to WiFi.

    config EGOS_STATUS_LED_ENABLED
        bool "Enable RGB status LED"
        default n
        help
            Enable RGB LED status indicator via LEDC PWM.
            Shows connection state through color patterns.

endmenu
